headline: Quarterra Begins Leasing at The Ansel, its Newest Multifamily Luxury Community in Texas
summary: Quarterra Multifamily, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a vertically integrated developer, property manager and asset manager, today announced the start of leasing at The Ansel, its newest luxury community in the heart of Texas.
